=== Hello, World!
My name is Hugo Coto Flórez. I'm a Spanish Computer Science student at the
University of Santiago de Compostela. In my free time I'm an artist, I write
prose that humans enjoy and compilers understand. I'm focused on being close to
the  hardware, while keeping programs as simple and performant as possible. I
read books about Operating Systems, Compilers or Linux just for fun. If you want
to see what I did, check Projects. For other writings as software or book
recommendations see Articles.

